column5: I'm sorry if this offended you in any way. Thank you so much for being so kind. C:
Thanks I needed that, have a great day.
Thank you, and best of luck to you too.

I think what you need to realize is that most people who are attracted to minors feel this same way. You feel like you're gonna hurt somebody, but reaility is you only hurt people if you want to hurt them. You should really tell a professional that you feel this way  . Because they can help you. You should know you're not fated to hurt anyone.
